snippet.title: SUDICE Gameplay
snippet.description:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.k3games.sudice

Choose your level.
Choose your time limit.
Swipe dices to roll them.
Double tap to lock dice if you are sure.
Solve the SUDICE and try to get the best score !
